node.text: Song Fa is my fav too 😊 their BKT goes perfect with their tau pok ❤️

Ordered islandwide delivery from @songfabkt for dinner! 
Hard to go wrong with this one.. Song Fa is one our favourite BKTs in Singapore :)
Like one of the staple food in sg, especially among the choices for BKTs in sg.
@karhingc oh me too! As u can tell I ordered it too haha
I Like their slices fish soup 😄😄😋
Song fa is my fav bkttttttt 😋
@foodirectory.sg hehe yup love the garlicky peppery taste 😋
Looove songfa too! its so garlicky 😋😋
@qingxiangsqx yea that’s good too. I like both wahaha
I still prefer the herbal bkt! 😋
@aaron_czh haha ya I was thinking that too. But luckily they gave a lot!
I’m so going here when I visit sg! 😍
Song Fa is my fav too 😊 their BKT goes perfect with their tau pok ❤️
